description: On Friday, CNN published footage that appears to show the hip-hop mogul, also known as P. Diddy, physically assaulting his then-girlfriend, Cassie Ventura, in a Los Angeles hotel in 2016.
title: Newly surfaced video shows apparent assault by Sean Combs like claims in settled case

description: More than 5,000 Mercedes-Benz workers who build luxury SUVs in Alabama were eligible to vote on whether to join the UAW. Workers faced intense anti-union messaging from Mercedes in the run-up.
title: Mercedes workers vote no to union, putting the brakes on UAW's march South

description: A shot of pure joy to start off the weekend: a charming video of kids from Cork, Ireland, rapping about finding and following their creative voice.
title: This wholesome banger from a group of Irish kids is the spark you need

description:

description: Speaking alongside brother/collaborator Finneas, Eilish says she discovered a new self-awareness on Hit Me Hard and Soft, after years of seeing herself through others' eyes.
title: Billie Eilish finally remembers who she is

description: Louisiana could be the first state to regulate mifepristone and misoprostol in the same way as some narcotics and stimulants. Opponents predict harmful delays in miscarriage and other lawful uses.
title: Louisiana may reclassify drugs used in abortion as controlled dangerous substances
